<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7797ba90-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s430tt"><num value="430tt">§ 430tt.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums, but not more than $722,000, as are necessary to carry out the provisions of sections 430pp to 430tt of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7797ba91-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/134/s5">Pub. L. 87–134, § 5</ref>, <date date="1961-08-10">Aug. 10, 1961</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/75/336">75 Stat. 336</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/93/477/tI/s101/4">Pub. L. 93–477, title I, § 101(4)</ref>, <date date="1974-10-26">Oct. 26, 1974</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/88/1445">88 Stat. 1445</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
